data.description: Looking for the privacy that comes along with country living while still being able to have the conveniences that come along with easy access to amenities? Look no further! This home is located in Holiday Village on .275 of an acre and is ready for a family! Home features a split floor plan with a large primary bedroom and two additional bedrooms. There is a lot of natural light throughout the home as well! The Kitchen is spacious and has open floor plan concept to the Living Room. Home also has a large front and back porch and two storage buildings. Neighborhood features gated entry access, pool, clubhouse, volleyball and basketball court! Come see everything that this home has to offer.
